data.description:
Imagine living in a World Class Prestigious Artificial Lagoon with proximity to everything - Schools, Mall, Gas, Groceries, Bank, Hospital, Day Care, Outlet mall and I-75. This exclusive enclave offers an unparalleled lifestyle, combining modern elegance with natural beauty. Situated right at the heart of the bustling town of Wesley Chapel Epperson Community, you will enjoy modern living with modern amenities. The jewel in the crown is the Crystal Lagoon itself a breathtaking, tropical oasis where residents can unwind by the shimmering waters, indulge in water sports, or simply bask in the sun on the pristine shore. Regular events and social gatherings foster a warm and welcoming atmosphere, creating opportunities for neighbors to connect and build lasting relationships. This community spirit enhances the overall living experience, turning each day into a delightful celebration of shared moments. Come home to the ultimate in luxury living at our rental property in the Crystal Lagoon Community. Discover a lifestyle where every detail is curated for your comfort, and where the beauty of nature converges with the sophistication of modern living. Welcome to your new home where luxury knows no bounds.

As the sun sets, the backyard becomes a haven of tranquility. Take a seat by the pond, where the soothing sounds of the fountains create a melody that complements the symphony of nature. The strategic east-facing orientation of the backyard ensures a comfortable and enjoyable experience, especially during parties and gatherings. Revel in the festivities without the discomfort of the evening sunlight's heat, creating the perfect environment for entertaining friends and family. Whether it's a barbecue, a casual get-together, or a celebration under the stars, the backyard provides an idyllic backdrop for memorable moments.

Immerse yourself in the beauty of the pond, where lush greenery and the gentle rippling of the water create a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. This outdoor retreat becomes your personal sanctuary, offering a space to reflect, unwind, and connect with the natural world.

In this idyllic location, every evening becomes a celebration of nature's beauty and the joy of shared moments. Whether you prefer quiet contemplation, the company of loved ones, or the excitement of a lively gathering, the backyard pond with its fountains is a captivating focal point that elevates your living experience to new heights. Welcome to a home where the magic of evenings is woven into the fabric of everyday life.

One year lease renewable annually. One month security deposit at contract signing and first month rent due on move in.

Tenant pays for Water, Electricity, Lawn maintenance, and Garbage. 

The rent includes high speed internet, About 200 TV channels, Lagoon access and HOA fees.
